Package yads.doi.lib

Class Summary
Authentication Class for manipulating authentication objects.
Common Class for common library constants.
Container Class for aggregating groups into containers.
DObject A DObject manages the resource hierarchy associated with a DOI public identifier.
DObjectInstance An instance of a library DObject for test purposes (see DObject.main(java.lang.String[])).
DObjectMap Class listing DObject map constants.
DObjectTypes Allowed DObject types and corresponding Handle types.
Group Class for aggregating data elements into groups.
Resource Convenience class for aggregating data elements into groups.
